data.description: Enjoy the serenity of mountain life in this quaint 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath home! A screened in porch area perfect for 3 season living greets you as you enter. This home features a large open living/dining space, perfect for spending time with family and friends. Enjoy numerous recent renovations including PERGO flooring in kitchen, living and dining room, plank ceilings throughout the entire downstairs, new kitchen cabinets and appliances and a new propane fireplace! This home is located only minutes to the Tuckaseegee River, Harrah's Cherokee Casino, the Smoky Mountain National Park, and the towns of Sylva and Bryson City!
